. A grove exists with several caretakers etc. The ancient Rehan religion does not have a direct place in the city, though there are of course believers with a grove to practice their religion. The thousand deities religion also has a small following in th
e
 city, some houses possessing shrines and religious items to praise these gods. It is fairly rare, and no Soldier may have such in his barracks. The only religion that a soldier may acceptably follow is the dual paths, though not many do. The religion bas
ed on the elements is followed similarly to the ancient Rehan religion \endash  that is there are some believers in the city, but no real practice of the religion.
